Barry'd Treasure was an American reality television series airing on A&E. The series premiered on March 18, 2014, and starred Barry Weiss in a spin-off of A&E's Storage Wars.
The series centered around Weiss (formerly a featured storage locker buyer on Storage Wars) as he traveled around the United States to find rare antiques and collectibles. The show also featured some of Weiss' previous Storage Wars sidekicks as they accompanied him on some of his travels.


